== Description ==

The [[Image:Assembly_ShowElementCS.svg|24px]] [[Assembly3_ShowElementCS|Show element coordinate system]] command toggles the visibility of '''element coordinate systems''' (ECSs).

An ECS is represented by 3 lines which meet at the elements origin:
* a red line for the X axis
* a green line for the Y axis
* a blue line for the Z axis

[[Image:Assembly3_ShowElementCS-01.png|300px]]

{{Caption|Element of a face with visible ECS}}

